structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
COUNTY GOVERNMENT (FISCAL COURTS AND COUNTY COMMISSIONERS)

law.catch_line: Receipt by county of urban library funds.
law.text: The fiscal court in any county in which there are no incorporated areas shall be eligible to receive urban libraries funds pursuant to KRS 173.860 and 173.870.
law.history: Created 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 327, sec. 3, effective July 15, 1988.
